Class TaskData.ExecutionPlan.Node

    public static class TaskData.ExecutionPlan.Node
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Each node represents a flow of DStreams in an application. Each node should produce only one kind of output. Note that an application may contain more than one node.

    Ken Yu, CRIPAC, 2016
